WEBVTT

00:00.183 --> 00:01.252
What's up guys, this is Justin.

00:01.435 --> 00:03.260
The typhoon affected the lives of millions.

00:03.559 --> 00:05.345
Everyone knows I've got the best fans in the world,...

00:05.703 --> 00:08.029
...so the moment I heard about the tragedy a few weeks back,...

00:08.598 --> 00:10.413
...I know I could count on you guys to make a difference.

00:10.817 --> 00:13.116
So I'm looking for you guys to help me help them.

00:13.295 --> 00:15.688
Check out prizeo.com/justin.

00:15.945 --> 00:18.706
In return for you giving back, I'm doing something I've never done before.

00:18.992 --> 00:21.921
I'm bringing a winner to come show him the studio with me next year.

00:22.089 --> 00:23.749
I want you guys to come help me in the studio.

00:23.834 --> 00:24.819
Give me some ideas.

00:25.436 --> 00:26.673
But first, you guys gotta give back.

00:27.369 --> 00:29.917
Help raise money and you can come in the studio with me.

00:30.381 --> 00:33.817
So please, please, help me help them.

